name: The Cubicle to CEO Podcast
what_you_do: Ellen Yin is a keynote speaker, podcast host, educator, and angel investor who helps entrepreneurs, particularly women, advance their economic opportunities through mentorship and education.
who_you_serve: Ellen serves primarily women entrepreneurs, providing them with resources, mentorship, and education to help them succeed in their business ventures.
bio: The podcast has been listened to 1 million times worldwide and Ellen has personally angel invested in three women-owned startups.
